// Base build settings for Dictly, wired as the project's base configuration
// (see Dictly.xcodeproj → target Debug/Release). Shared, public-safe settings
// belong here.
//
// Personal / local-only overrides — notably your code-signing DEVELOPMENT_TEAM —
// live in Local.xcconfig, which is gitignored. The optional include below is
// silently skipped when that file is absent (e.g. for an external contributor),
// so they simply sign with their own team in Xcode.
#include? "Local.xcconfig"
